# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:13
translate spanish jez1_2233ac4e:

    # "My phone rings, waking me up. I look at the screen and it says Detective Rodriguez."
    "Suena mi teléfono, despertándome. Miro la pantalla y pone «Detective Rodríguez»."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:14
translate spanish jez1_bea5e8cb:

    # pc "Hello?"
    pc "¿Hola?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:15
translate spanish jez1_bca81714:

    # det "Hello, is this [pcname]?"
    det "Hola, ¿eres [pcname]?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:16
translate spanish jez1_6dba6230:

    # pc "Yes."
    pc "Sí."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:17
translate spanish jez1_adbdbbea:

    # det "Are you at home?"
    det "¿Estás en casa?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:18
translate spanish jez1_6dba6230_1:

    # pc "Yes."
    pc "Sí."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:19
translate spanish jez1_14ff57f7:

    # det "Okay, I'm almost at your house. I got approval to unlock the basement for you, so I'm bringing over the key now."
    det "Vale, ya casi estoy en tu casa. Me han dado permiso para abrirte el sótano, así que te traigo la llave ahora mismo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:20
translate spanish jez1_9979ad0e:

    # pc "Great."
    pc "Genial."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:21
translate spanish jez1_2ebb04fd:

    # det "Be there in two minutes."
    det "Estaré allí en dos minutos."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:22
translate spanish jez1_b05a4fa4:

    # "She hangs up the phone."
    "Cuelga el teléfono."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:25
translate spanish jez1_82a5849a:

    # "I quickly get dressed and head downstairs. As soon as I open the front door, I see her walking quickly up the walkway towards the door."
    "Me visto rápidamente y bajo las escaleras. En cuanto abro la puerta principal, la veo caminando rápidamente por el camino de entrada hacia la puerta."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:28
translate spanish jez1_697391b1:

    # det "Sorry I don't really have time to talk at the moment, but here is the key to the basement."
    det "Lo siento, no tengo tiempo para hablar ahora mismo, pero aquí tienes la llave del sótano."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:30
translate spanish jez1_7c67e994:

    # det "There's nothing new on the case right now. I'll let you know as soon as any progress happens."
    det "No hay nada nuevo en el caso por el momento. Te avisaré en cuanto haya algún avance."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:32
translate spanish jez1_39cf2074:

    # det "And you let me know if you find anything down there in that basement. You are probably the best person to look through it, as you understand a little more about his job than any of our people."
    det "Y avísame si encuentras algo ahí abajo, en el sótano. Probablemente seas la persona más indicada para registrarlo, ya que entiendes un poco más de su trabajo que cualquiera de nuestra gente."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:33
translate spanish jez1_5c2df0f8:

    # det "You will tell me if you find anything right?"
    det "Me dirás si encuentras algo, ¿verdad?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:37
translate spanish jez1_fc19b673:

    # det "Good."
    det "Bien."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:40
translate spanish jez1_37971de3:

    # det "You better. It's important that you cooperate."
    det "Más te vale. Es importante que cooperes."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:42
translate spanish jez1_15fe2f48:

    # det "Okay, well I have to run. Talk to you again soon."
    det "Vale, bueno, tengo que irme. Hablamos pronto."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:44
translate spanish jez1_4ced5b36:

    # "She quickly turns and rushes back out to her car and drives away."
    "Se da la vuelta rápidamente, sale corriendo hacia su coche y se marcha."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:46
translate spanish jez1_39aad490:

    # "I turn and look at the basement door, holding the key to it in my hand."
    "Me giro y miro la puerta del sótano, con la llave en la mano."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:47
translate spanish jez1_5b0ca9d0:

    # "When I slide the key in and hear the click of it unlock, I can't help but feel that I'm doing something wrong."
    "Cuando introduzco la llave y oigo el clic al abrirla, no puedo evitar sentir que estoy haciendo algo malo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:48
translate spanish jez1_cef55c67:

    # "Even though I'm an adult, even though Dad's not down there, the basement still looks somehow menacing and forbidden."
    "Aunque soy adulto, aunque papá no esté ahí abajo, el sótano sigue pareciendo de alguna manera amenazador y prohibido."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:49
translate spanish jez1_3a110456:

    # "The rest of the family was never allowed to come down here or to disturb him while he was working."
    "Al resto de la familia nunca se nos permitía bajar aquí ni molestarle mientras trabajaba."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez1.rpy:51
translate spanish jez1_39472555:

    # "I feel a pit in my stomach as I turn the handle and open the door."
    "Siento un nudo en el estómago al girar el pomo y abrir la puerta."

